    {"id":"KB-008","mode":"interactive","title":"ACP-4000 / IPC-610 风扇检查与更换","baseVersion":"1.0","equipment":"ACP-4000 / IPC-610","faultType":"风扇异常","verificationLevel":"verified_case","applicability":"exact_model","summary":"结合 TEMP/FAN 告警、转速与温度阈值，完成滤网、风道、风扇和 FAN 接线检查，并在清理无效时更换故障风扇。","baseContent":"检查风扇状态、FAN1/FAN2 接线和供电，必要时更换同规格风扇。","publishedContentV11":"当 TEMP/FAN 告警、风扇转速低于 500 rpm 同时出现，且清理风道与滤网后转速仍未恢复，应重点判断风扇老化，并在断电、挂牌和防静电确认后检查或更换风扇。","sourceRefs":[{"documentId":"DOC-ADVANTECH-ACP4000-IPC610-UM-ED6","pages":[32,33,39,40,41]},{"documentId":"DOC-ADVANTECH-ACP4000-DS-20250317","pages":[1,2]},{"documentId":"DOC-ADVANTECH-IPC610H-DS-20221006","pages":[1,2]},{"documentId":"DOC-ADVANTECH-IPC610L-IPC611-DS-20221006","pages":[1,2]},{"documentId":"DOC-ADVANTECH-SAB2000-SM-ED2","pages":[1,2,3]}]},
